Try this celery.

193
00:19:05,670 --> 00:19:06,510
Rose,

194
00:19:10,230 --> 00:19:12,060
do you remember what you said to me

195
00:19:13,860 --> 00:19:15,950
the night I lost my job?

196
00:19:17,580 --> 00:19:18,710
I told you to start over.

197
00:19:18,910 --> 00:19:19,750
And what else?

198
00:19:23,140 --> 00:19:24,910
Whatever you do, I'll support you.

199
00:19:27,860 --> 00:19:28,700
Just...

200
00:19:28,990 --> 00:19:30,750
Just what you said to me

201
00:19:31,540 --> 00:19:32,580
that night I lost my job.

202
00:19:33,990 --> 00:19:34,830
Do you remember?

203
00:20:13,190 --> 00:20:14,140
In this card,

204
00:20:15,300 --> 00:20:16,300
