205
00:20:20,540 --> 00:20:22,140
This is a copy

206
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:23,930
of the company's business license.

207
00:20:24,270 --> 00:20:26,950
Inside are the official seals
for finance and contracts.

208
00:20:28,270 --> 00:20:29,300
This USB contains

209
00:20:29,670 --> 00:20:31,710
all the financial records up to today.

210
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:37,540
Do you want reimbursements from me?

211
00:20:43,470 --> 00:20:45,990
This is everything I have.

212
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:48,950
My life and all

213
00:20:49,950 --> 00:20:50,790
are entrusted to you.

214
00:20:57,510 --> 00:20:58,640
The company has already secured

215
00:20:59,030 --> 00:20:59,870
two projects.

216
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:01,910
They're not huge,

217
00:21:02,580 --> 00:21:04,100
but they can make some money.

218
00:21:04,620 --> 00:21:05,990
Every penny I earn in the future

219
00:21:05,990 --> 00:21:06,950
will also be given to you.

220
00:21:07,270 --> 00:21:09,580
A house, a car, and everything
will be under your name.

221
00:21:16,470 --> 00:21:17,310
Huang Yimei,

222
00:21:18,950 --> 00:21:19,820
