223
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,540
What day is it?

224
00:21:32,380 --> 00:21:34,100
Today isn't any special day.

225
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:36,620
Originally, I planned

226
00:21:38,430 --> 00:21:40,270
to wait until the company had developed

227
00:21:41,470 --> 00:21:42,540
with a certain foundation,

228
00:21:42,950 --> 00:21:44,380
so I could be good enough
to propose to you.

229
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:46,950
But I just can't wait anymore.

230
00:21:49,230 --> 00:21:50,070
Of course,

231
00:21:50,910 --> 00:21:52,340
for someone like me, a poor guy,

232
00:21:53,190 --> 00:21:55,230
to propose to you shamelessly like this,

233
00:21:56,430 --> 00:21:57,620
if you don't want to,

234
00:21:58,750 --> 00:21:59,590
I can understand.

235
00:22:06,140 --> 00:22:07,380
- Do you love me?
- Of course.

236
00:22:07,710 --> 00:22:08,550
For what?

237
00:22:08,710 --> 00:22:09,550
I love you

238
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:12,670
for your kindness, intelligence,
and loveliness.

239
00:22:14,580 --> 00:22:16,750
Anyway, you're the best woman
in my heart.

240
00:22:17,620 --> 00:22:18,910
No, goddess.

241
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:28,950
I love you too.

242
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:30,990
I think

243
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:33,780
you're talented, responsible,

244
00:22:34,750 --> 00:22:35,590
and ambitious.

245
00:22:36,380 --> 00:22:38,750
They say the only condition for marriage

246
00:22:38,860 --> 00:22:39,780
is to genuinely admire

247
00:22:41,100 --> 00:22:44,100
and love each other.

248
00:22:48,140 --> 00:22:49,140
So will you agree?

249
00:22:51,580 --> 00:22:52,420
I love you.

250
00:23:07,710 --> 00:23:08,550
Rose.

251
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:11,140
