334
00:29:17,940 --> 00:29:18,790
Of course.

335
00:29:18,820 --> 00:29:19,820
Have you thought about it?

336
00:29:20,620 --> 00:29:22,340
Two people marry out of true love.

337
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:23,990
They accompany each other
