377
00:31:19,710 --> 00:31:20,550
Would you like to do that?

378
00:31:20,860 --> 00:31:21,700
Of course.

379
00:31:21,990 --> 00:31:22,860
Absolutely.

380
00:31:23,140 --> 00:31:25,430
