00:31:56,230 --> 00:31:57,140
to her.

391
00:31:58,860 --> 00:31:59,780
Why now?

392
00:32:06,910 --> 00:32:07,750
I don't know either.

393
00:32:09,860 --> 00:32:10,700
Maybe

394
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,430
I was afraid of losing her.

395
00:32:14,780 --> 00:32:15,620
I know

396
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:17,110
there have always been

397
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:19,510
people better off than me by her side.

398
00:32:20,540 --> 00:32:22,470
I have no money or a house.

399
00:32:23,430 --> 00:32:24,860
I just bought a used car

400
00:32:25,780 --> 00:32:27,470
and it's used by everyone in the company.

401
00:32:31,100 --> 00:32:31,940
I...

402
00:32:33,380 --> 00:32:34,430
I did consider

403
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:36,820
saving more money

404
00:32:37,580 --> 00:32:38,510
before proposing to her.

405
00:32:39,060 --> 00:32:39,950
But I'm just afraid.

406
00:32:43,710 --> 00:32:44,550
I'm afraid

407
00:32:44,670 --> 00:32:45,670
a long delay may cause trouble.

408
00:32:47,990 --> 00:32:49,780
Ms. Su, please believe me.

409
00:32:50,580 --> 00:32:52,990
I will do my utmost to make her happy.

410
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:53,940
Really.

411
00:32:55,470 --> 00:32:56,620
I'm not questioning you.

412
00:32:56,620 --> 00:32:57,910
And you don't need to assure me.

413
00:32:58,780 --> 00:33:00,470
I just want to remind you of one thing.

414
00:33:01,780 --> 00:33:02,620
What is it?

415
00:33:02,860 --> 00:33:03,700
Don't feel inferior.

416
00:33:04,910 --> 00:33:06,540
You and I have a business relationship,

417
00:33:06,860 --> 00:33:08,670
but you and Yimei don't.

418
00:33:08,860 --> 00:33:10,140
When two people are together,

419
00:33:10,140 --> 00:33:11,750
if we still talk about qualifications,

420
00:33:11,780 --> 00:33:13,540
compare bids and the like,

421
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:15,540
that's not love.

422
00:33:16,060 --> 00:33:17,030
You have to believe

423
00:33:17,620 --> 00:33:19,100
since she chose you,

424
00:33:19,540 --> 00:33:20,950
you have no competition.

425
00:33:22,190 --> 00:33:23,750
Inferiority is a double-edged sword.

426
00:33:24,670 --> 00:33:26,510
It can motivate you

427
00:33:26,750 --> 00:33:28,540
but also make you sensitive and fragile.

428
00:33:28,540 --> 00:33:29,510
It will throw you off balance.

429
00:33:31,750 --> 00:33:32,710
Don't let it control you.

430
00:33:37,510 --> 00:33:38,350
I understand.

431
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:40,700
Ms. Su,

432
00:33:41,540 --> 00:33:42,380
thank you.

433
00:33:58,710 --> 00:33:59,550
Look.

434
00:33:59,710 --> 00:34:01,750
