460
00:34:59,180 --> 00:35:00,540
Should we put this here?

461
00:35:00,540 --> 00:35:01,390
Put it here.

462
00:35:01,390 --> 00:35:02,350
Put it here, here.

463
00:35:02,350 --> 00:35:03,520
Give it to me.

464
00:35:03,540 --> 00:35:04,380
Okay.

465
00:35:04,390 --> 00:35:05,470
We've got their backs.

466
00:35:05,620 --> 00:35:07,060
Let the kids go and explore.

467
00:35:07,830 --> 00:35:10,220
It's their prime time.

468
00:35:10,390 --> 00:35:11,930
They've never suffered
since they were little.

469
00:35:13,030 --> 00:35:14,660
As long as it's reasonable,

470
00:35:15,030 --> 00:35:16,830
